			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>Augt 23d 5612</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Rev &#38; Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">You will please to notice in the occident of<lb/> the next month that <persName>Mr. S.&#59; Sedgwick</persName> Principal of the Methenal<add>&#63;</add><lb/> &#38; Class&#58; Institute has <sic>purched</sic> two lots of ground being <placeName>93 &#38; 95<lb/> <sic>Sixt</sic> Av</placeName>&#58; on which lots a building is in erecting of 100 by 50 feet<lb/> a 5 Stories house&#44; which building <sic>building</sic> when completed<lb/> will a splendid one and will <add>&#63;</add> any School or College<lb/> in the <placeName>United States</placeName>&#44; There will be <add>&#63;</add> 1 a lecture Room<lb/> a debating Room for the discussion of Hebr Literature<lb/> 2 Gymnasiums&#44; 3d School Room&#44; 4th languages &#38; 5th a Hebr<lb/> Department.  The instructions will comprise</p>
				<p>Engl&#58; Litar&#44; Modrn Litar&#58; Lat&#58; &#38; Greek &#38; <add>&#63;</add></p>
				<p>Drawing &#38; Arts of Design&#44; Methen&#58; &#38; Michan.</p>
				<p>Philosop &#38; Astron Chemis&#58; &#38; Physic&#58;</p>
				<p>Mor&#58; intellet &#38; Ph<add>&#63;</add> Phil</p>
				<p>  Hebr <add>&#63;</add> <add>&#63;</add> Arab&#58; &#38; <add>&#63;</add> languages</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">  There will be engaged 8 Proff. Of the 1st class</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">  The whole will be a splendid affair&#44; &#38; I</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">  hope when in town to visit it&#59; it will be</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">  ready in the <date>15th of Sept</date> <add>&#63;</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">yours Truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><persName role="author">Simon C Nool</persName></p>
				<p>N B we had the gratification last <date>Sabbath</date> that one of our<lb/> pupils of the school of my Congn gave <sic>prove</sic> of <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> the boy being only 11 years of age&#44; is fully competent to act<lb/> as <add>Hebrew</add> in my congn.</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
